general.desc: GHL Systems Bhd is a Malaysian company that acts as a payment services provider having its business operations in Malaysia, Philippines, Thailand, Indonesia, Cambodia, and Australia. The operating segments of the company are Shared Services, Solution Services, and Transaction Payment Acquisition. Shared Services comprise the sale, rental, and maintenance of EDC terminals and other card-acceptance devices. Solution Services comprises the sale and maintenance of hardware devices and software. Transaction Payment Acquisition comprises e-pay services which include telco prepaid and other top-up facilities and bill collection services for consumers as well as electronic payment services. The majority of the company's revenue comes from the Philippines.
general.short_desc: GHL Systems Bhd is engaged in developing & selling in-house software programs & provides end-to-end payment solutions. It is also engaged in the sale & rental of Electronic Data Capture equipment & related software & services.
